{"tid":678442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係屋企人或許多年兄弟, 普通朋友同學同事都唔好信到足","createTime":"2018-05-26T05:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T06:35:17.000Z","uid":95393,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0cd0c872577ff75a2a150924def8c580601c38ba","tid":678442,"uid":95393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T05:43:17.000Z","msg":"特別講到關錢事既就乜嘢人性黑暗面都睇到晒<br />\n<br />\n分享一個朋友既case<br />\n<br />\n［裝修老千］呢個人叫何德昕（Ho Tak Yan, Eric), （電話：64389693）同本人為中學同學關係相識有十幾年，3月尾將新公司裝修裝修工程判左比佢做，由於同學關係係工程第一次比錢時無簽署文件（話遲下補番），後來更以佢公司調轉不靈，向我收取工程尾數。事後工程不停延期（約18/5），由於覺得事有蹊蹺，於是我搵其他裝修師父上去驗查，一驗發現原來係化妝樓。Eric Ho 知道事件被拆穿後再沒有回覆本人（至24/5），前後裝修費超過40萬，由於本人得知，Eric Ho 在我裝修工程期間依然有接Job, 所以為免更多人受害，請廣傳！事後佢公司Facebook 專頁已刪除了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/charm.chan.9/posts/10156264446232226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcharm.chan.9%2Fposts%2F10156264446232226&d=j0YDAcivOU%2FYqdyyERvDj49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=a68aab16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/charm.chan.9/posts/10156264446232226</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/131804_eecc0e8bf4fc275233e016c4e773ab0c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F131804_eecc0e8bf4fc275233e016c4e773ab0c.png&h=7c45a746&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/131805_c4c4991310cee8135a22380b69749ae3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F131805_c4c4991310cee8135a22380b69749ae3.png&h=1a25c20e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/131808_e3c50fc3756fb9f974a591b5637c2267.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F131808_e3c50fc3756fb9f974a591b5637c2267.png&h=31eecc2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/131811_39daa1f158a946ada582e0207a0339a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F131811_39daa1f158a946ada582e0207a0339a2.png&h=575fedc6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/131812_80c749634e1b6b645188019efa4663cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F131812_80c749634e1b6b645188019efa4663cf.png&h=ce5f109e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/131814_d716c6d1d0e72d4748d20d1a51abd7d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F131814_d716c6d1d0e72d4748d20d1a51abd7d5.png&h=e2929992&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/131816_5e42b7e5f83bf7f5445cde4f7a3188da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F131816_5e42b7e5f83bf7f5445cde4f7a3188da.png&h=abc7dd3d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/131818_b1c57631ebe43673b3cb4316a21c3191.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F131818_b1c57631ebe43673b3cb4316a21c3191.png&h=82636474&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/131821_5e26038bd1bcc3d2f957e769e97e194f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F131821_5e26038bd1bcc3d2f957e769e97e194f.png&h=b4c87cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外仲有一個朋友去搵舊同事間財仔借錢, 律師樓做交易, 結果錢交左(仲要現金) 樓按埋, 律師樓兩個禮拜後執左舊同事失蹤仲欠債過百萬<br />\n<br />\n有時真係個信字出事<br />\n好多騙徒老千就專睇中d 有少少關係又拎到信任既人落手<br />\n唔熟唔食, 有錢就咩都做得出"},{"pid":"c1fceeb7c8e815a3901e1dea37104b2de4340377","tid":678442,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"屋企人都會出賣你啦。傻豬黎既。"},{"pid